    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Austrocarabodes vernoncrookensis sp. nov. A—Dorsal view with magnifications of lamellar seta (le) and sensillus (ss). B—detail of notogastral seta (dm) and ornamentation on notogaster. C—Ventral view. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183283/files/figure.png" ;
